###L4 Sub-Dimension Mapping

1. L4_Simplification_stepwise
Corresponds to: Senior-focused simplification & stepwise guidance

2. L4_Motor_voice_accessibility
Corresponds to: Senior motor & voice accessibility options (voice input, large targets, reduced precision)

3. L4_Plain_language_readability
Corresponds to: Plain-language & readability thresholds met (senior-appropriate)

4. L4_Cognitive_load_reduction
Corresponds to: Cognitive-load reduction patterns (chunking, progressive disclosure)
